Yeah. Besides pharmacy, there are other easier majors.

39
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:48,640
- Yes. 
 - It's not that stressful.

40
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:50,840
And the admission score is lower. You'll get in for sure.

41
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,897
Yes.

42
00:02:51,897 --> 00:02:55,080
Why am I only applying to this university? I want to check out others.

43
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:57,040
- Others are fine too. 
 - Look.

44
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:59,160
This one. My scores are enough for this.

45
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,200
- No. 
 - Not okay.

46
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:02,830
Their campus environment is average.

47
00:03:02,830 --> 00:03:04,950
- Yes. 
 - Wait.

48
00:03:04,950 --> 00:03:06,520
How did you know?

49
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,320
We've investigated it thoroughly.

50
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:11,700
- Yeah. 
 - We don't think this university is good.

51
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,640
- What about this one? I can get into this. 
 - No.

52
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:20,180
This is not good either. It's hard to graduate from this school.

53
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,970
- Yes. 
 - And the schoolwork pressure is too much.

54
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:23,980
No.

55
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:27,460
- This one then. I heard that this— 
 - No.

56
00:03:27,460 --> 00:03:29,670
Look at the name of this major. It's really weird.

57
00:03:29,670 --> 00:03:31,060
I think you won't be able to find a job.

58
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:32,920
- Right? 
 - Yes.

59
00:03:36,450 --> 00:03:39,300
Wait. What's going on?

60
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:42,070
So I can only apply to universities within the province and not outside?

61
00:03:42,070 --> 00:03:43,780
No.

62
00:03:43,780 --> 00:03:46,450
She's asking you. What's going on?

63
00:03:46,450 --> 00:03:48,950
She's asking you.

64
00:03:48,950 --> 00:03:51,340
Dad, what's going on?

65
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:52,890
No, Huan Er. Well...

66
00:03:52,890 --> 00:03:55,900
It's not that we're forcing you to go to universities in the province.

67
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:59,500
- Yes. 
 - It's mainly because we're a little worried.

68
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:04,270
Think about it. If you have a headache, I can come over immediately.

69
00:04:04,270 --> 00:04:08,900
Besides, if I can't go, Aunt Hao Mei, Aunt Yi Fan, and Uncle Song can come over.

70
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,110
- Yes. 
 - You...

71
00:04:10,110 --> 00:04:11,550
I...

72
00:04:11,550 --> 00:04:13,070
If you're far away...

73
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:15,490
- If you're sick... 
 - Don't cry.

74
00:04:15,490 --> 00:04:20,820
- Calm down. 
 - If you're really sick, I can't see you...

75
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:22,980
even if I want to take care of you.

76
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:25,720
All right.

77
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:28,940
Actually, universities outside the province aren't bad either.

78
00:04:28,940 --> 00:04:33,060
It's just... I don't know how you'll manage.

79
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,740
Mom, I'm just going to university.

80
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:36,550
I'll come back often, okay?

81
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:37,860
Okay?

82
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:39,550
Don't cry.

83
00:04:39,550 --> 00:04:43,860
If there's no other way, I... I'll apply to Anhui University, okay?

84
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:46,660
Anhui University?

85
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:48,820
- Anhui University is actually quite good. 
 - Yes.

86
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:49,800
- Really. 
 - Yes.

87
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,740
I think Anhui University is good.

88
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:55,460
What would you like to eat? I'll make it for you right away.

89
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:57,930
Let's go.

90
00:04:57,930 --> 00:05:00,010
Hurry.

91
00:05:08,930 --> 00:05:10,860
How comfortable.

92
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:14,700
How did you all fill out your university applications?

93
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:17,130
Jing Xi Chi.

94
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:21,590
I haven't made up my mind.

95
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:23,180
I'm lost.

96
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,890
Cong, what about you?

97
00:05:26,890 --> 00:05:30,160
I'm considering whether to apply to Tianhe University.

98
00:05:33,590 --> 00:05:36,550
With these scores, you're applying to Tianhe University?

99
00:05:36,550 --> 00:05:38,380
Why don't you go to Yenching University?

100
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:41,740
It's near home. I can take care of my mom.

101
00:05:43,890 --> 00:05:45,960
No. Your mom has your dad to take care of her.

102
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,620
Besides, Aunt Hao has almost recovered.

103
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:50,380
Haven't you always wanted to go to the Medical School of Yenching University?

104
00:06:02,570 --> 00:06:05,080
Cong, why do I feel like you've changed?

105
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,050
You weren't like this before.

106
00:06:07,050 --> 00:06:08,960
You were the one full of ideas.

107
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:12,480
Out of all three years of middle school, you're the one who had the most going on.

108
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:15,260
You were the one who transferred classes. You even transferred schools.

109
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:18,036
And you kept saying you wanted to study medicine.

110
00:06:18,036 --> 00:06:19,760
What’s happened to you now?

111
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,060
Yeah, Cong.

112
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:23,016
I think Jing Xi Chi's right.

113
00:06:23,016 --> 00:06:27,520
You can't give in just because you're afraid to tell your mom you want to study medicine.

114
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,970
Enough about me.

115
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:36,280
What about you?

116
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:39,760
Me?

117
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:47,120
A captive bird like me will probably never be able to escape the cage of my mom's love.

118
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,420
What do you mean?

119
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:51,930
It means my mom wants me to apply to Anhui University,

120
00:06:51,930 --> 00:06:55,380
saying it's close and convenient for her to take care of me.

121
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,640
Cong, she's teasing you.

122
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:01,160
Don't sow discord.

123
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:05,800
Cong. That's not what I meant.

124
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:09,930
I really think you need to think it through again.

125
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:19,260
I'll talk to my mom.

126
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:20,590
Go.

127
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:28,560
What about you?

128
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:31,340
Are you really going to give in to your mom?

129
00:07:32,010 --> 00:07:34,370
Not really.

130
00:07:34,370 --> 00:07:38,230
I think that Anhui University is the most suitable.

131
00:07:38,230 --> 00:07:42,440
Besides, I didn't have any ideas about the future.

132
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:44,580
I was just taking things one step at a time.

133
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:51,740
But I didn't expect your score to be so much higher than mine.

134
00:07:52,550 --> 00:07:56,640
Didn't Mr. Xu say that grades can't determine your life?

135
00:07:58,940 --> 00:08:02,610
But they can decide that we have fun this summer.

136
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:05,400
How about we go out and have fun this weekend?

137
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:07,040
Sure. Where are we going?

138
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,400
Who do you want to invite?

139
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:10,400
Just tell me who you don't want to invite.

140
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:13,010
I don't want to invite you.

141
00:08:13,010 --> 00:08:14,520
Master of sarcasm.

142
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:16,230
- No. 
 - You're stubborn.

143
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:17,860
- No. 
 - Go on being stubborn.

144
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:20,060
- No. 
 - You're still stubborn.

145
00:08:25,130 --> 00:08:27,060
You're back.

146
00:08:44,990 --> 00:08:46,520
What's wrong?

147
00:08:53,090 --> 00:08:58,430
Mom, I want to discuss university applications with you.

148
00:09:00,260 --> 00:09:02,170
No need to discuss.

149
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:05,530
I've already discussed it with your dad.

150
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:13,460
We'll enroll you in the Medical School of Yenching University.

151
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:16,900
Medical school?

152
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:20,740
What's wrong? Haven't you always wanted to study medicine?

153
00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:22,710
How did you know?

154
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:27,680
You're my son. How could I not know?

155
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:29,860
You're always secretly reading your dad's medical books.

156
00:09:29,860 --> 00:09:31,700
I already noticed.

157
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:35,710
You two, father and son, really never give me a moment of peace.

158
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:39,740
One says he wants to quit smoking but ends up smoking secretly in the kitchen every day.

159
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:42,780
He doesn't even clean up the ashes after smoking.

160
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:47,330
The other insists on studying medicine.

161
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,030
You two teamed up to lie to me.

162
00:09:56,740 --> 00:09:58,630
Sorry, Mom.

163
00:10:00,310 --> 00:10:02,180
Enough.

164
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:04,400
Why are you apologizing?

165
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:12,430
Let go.

166
00:10:17,260 --> 00:10:19,170
Let go.

167
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:29,920
I know why you want to stay in Tianhe.

168
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:34,990
I'm recovering well now.

169
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:37,860
I don't need you to take care of me.

170
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:41,400
I don't want to be a burden to any of you.

171
00:10:41,970 --> 00:10:46,760
If you stay here for me, I will feel guilty for the rest of my life. You know?

172
00:10:54,610 --> 00:10:56,470
Son.

173
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:03,780
You'll always make me proud.

174
00:11:04,990 --> 00:11:07,860
Your world can't be limited to just this place.

175
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:27,230
- Mom. 
 - Don't do it.

176
