Here, fruit and milk.

179
00:12:10,345 --> 00:12:11,500
Drink some.

180
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,900
Rest early. Stop looking at the computer.

181
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:15,260
Mom.

182
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:18,380
Tell me which university I should apply to.

183
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:20,760
It's up to you. I support you no matter what.

184
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:23,230
Even if you repeat a year and retake the exam, I support you.

185
00:12:23,230 --> 00:12:24,950
But you have to help me think it through!

186
00:12:24,950 --> 00:12:28,120
Other parents are concerned about this.

187
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,593
Really?

188
00:12:29,593 --> 00:12:32,620
If I make the decision, will you listen to me?

189
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:35,090
You can't just leave me to figure it out on my own...

190
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:38,160
You've grown up.

191
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:40,010
I trust your decision.

192
00:12:40,010 --> 00:12:43,590
You'll definitely choose the major that suits you best.

193
00:12:43,590 --> 00:12:48,310
With your current score, even the worst school isn't bad.

194
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:58,530
 Just let him study whatever he wants to study. 

195
00:12:58,530 --> 00:13:00,960
 Enough said. Let's be realistic. 

196
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,760
 At least if he studies something medical, 

197
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:04,440
 I can help him build some connections. 

198
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,380
 Won't that be good? 

199
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:08,950
 Go and tell him then. 

200
00:13:08,950 --> 00:13:10,740
 I won't tell him. 

