00:15:32,140 --> 00:15:34,230
I can't stand it anymore.

213
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:37,310
What a lousy place Jing Xi Chi picked.

214
00:15:37,310 --> 00:15:39,440
Even cars can't get up here!

215
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:44,950
How is this a graduation trip?

216
00:15:44,950 --> 00:15:46,780
Isn't this military training?

217
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:48,540
Qi Qi.

218
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:51,540
What's in your bag? It looks heavy.

219
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:53,710
I packed some movie DVDs...

220
00:15:53,710 --> 00:15:57,130
Who knew we would be hiking?

221
00:15:57,130 --> 00:15:59,950
No, I can't hike anymore.

222
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:01,910
I need a break.

223
00:16:04,180 --> 00:16:06,080
I can't hike anymore either.

224
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:09,700
Whoever wants to hike can go ahead.

225
00:16:12,190 --> 00:16:15,910
Let me call them to pick us up.

226
00:16:20,710 --> 00:16:22,110
How's it going?

227
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:23,330
No one's picking up...

228
00:16:23,330 --> 00:16:25,310
I'll call Li Tian.

229
00:16:25,990 --> 00:16:28,340
I'll call Song Cong then.

230
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:36,500
Are we really not answering?

231
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,270
No need.

232
00:16:39,620 --> 00:16:41,790
Would they really be fine?

233
00:16:42,470 --> 00:16:45,073
I can guess what Chen Huan Er is going to say.

234
00:16:45,073 --> 00:16:46,920
Jing Xi Chi, are you out of your mind?

235
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:49,140
Jing Xi Chi, what a lousy place you picked.

236
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:51,850
Jing Xi Chi, come pick us up.

237
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:55,140
We should just go pick it up.

238
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:56,820
Go ahead then.

239
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:04,050
 Jing Xi Chi, are you out of your mind? 

240
00:17:04,050 --> 00:17:05,770
 What a lousy place you picked. 

241
00:17:05,770 --> 00:17:08,540
 I'll give you one minute to come down and pick us up. 

242
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:10,390
 You hear me? 

243
00:17:10,390 --> 00:17:13,570
 Hello? Say something. 

244
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:18,230
Victory is just ahead. Good luck. We'll wait for you.

245
00:17:18,230 --> 00:17:19,860
Hello?

246
00:17:21,850 --> 00:17:24,050
He hung up on me.

247
00:17:28,230 --> 00:17:30,440
He's doomed.

248
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:34,810
When the three of them arrive, we'll set off some fireworks to surprise them.

249
00:17:34,810 --> 00:17:36,164
- Sure. 
 - You're almost done blowing it, right?

250
00:17:36,164 --> 00:17:37,460
Wash the fruits.

251
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:40,720
Jing Xi Chi, did you call me here just to make me do the hard labor?

252
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,760
What's the matter? You want to leave?

253
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,480
Go home and continue to be scolded?

254
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:46,630
Fine.

255
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:48,470
I'll wash them for you now.

256
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:52,100
See? I told you not to invite him... he's so petty.

257
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:53,820
All he does is whine.

258
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:56,320
 Jing Xi Chi, do I need to wash these oranges? 

259
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:58,390
