 - I'll choose one.

438
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:41,600
I'll choose the piglet.

439
00:29:41,600 --> 00:29:42,640
It really looks like you.

440
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,843
Burping and farting.

441
00:29:44,843 --> 00:29:47,760
