471
00:31:17,940 --> 00:31:19,030
- Come on. 
 - Come on.

472
00:31:19,030 --> 00:31:20,280
- Together. 
 - Cheers.

473
00:31:20,280 --> 00:31:21,810
- Cheers. 
 - Cheers.

474
00:31:21,810 --> 00:31:24,620
