00:34:27,160 --> 00:34:29,280
How long have we known each other?

533
00:34:34,660 --> 00:34:36,620
Quite a long time.

534
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:38,790
What's wrong?

535
00:34:38,790 --> 00:34:41,960
Then you should know what kind of person I am.

536
00:34:50,620 --> 00:34:55,270
If you ask me about others, I'm really not too sure.

537
00:34:55,270 --> 00:34:57,550
But you...

538
00:34:59,310 --> 00:35:05,850
You're just a big bad wolf in sheep's clothing.

539
00:35:09,270 --> 00:35:10,790
Yes.

540
00:35:12,020 --> 00:35:16,350
Since I was little, I always worked hard to get what I wanted.

541
00:35:16,350 --> 00:35:18,300
But it's different this time.

542
00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:22,460
I've been holding back.

543
00:35:27,020 --> 00:35:30,060
Because you're my best friend.

544
00:35:30,060 --> 00:35:33,600
So here's a question I have to ask you.

545
00:35:41,390 --> 00:35:43,480
Do you like Chen Huan Er?

546
00:36:01,180 --> 00:36:02,860
Huan Er.

547
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:05,930
I like Song Cong.

548
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:16,300
Actually, I already knew.

549
00:36:18,660 --> 00:36:20,620
Is it that obvious?

550
00:36:20,620 --> 00:36:23,670
No, it's not.

551
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:28,370
Actually,

552
00:36:29,450 --> 00:36:31,590
it's quite obvious.

553
00:36:35,790 --> 00:36:37,470
I know.

554
00:36:41,170 --> 00:36:43,060
Do you like Song Cong?

555
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:45,470
Song Cong and I?

556
00:36:45,470 --> 00:36:48,120
We're just friends.

557
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:54,210
Well...

558
00:36:54,990 --> 00:37:01,190
In your eyes, are Song Cong and Jing Xi Chi the same kind of friends to you?

559
00:37:03,910 --> 00:37:05,400
Let me ask this.

560
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:08,520
If Song Cong and Jing Xi Chi fell into the water at the same time,

561
00:37:08,520 --> 00:37:10,700
who would you save first?

562
00:37:11,790 --> 00:37:14,100
That's such a cheesy question.

563
00:37:14,100 --> 00:37:16,280
What is this, the Stone Age?

564
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:18,060
Answer it seriously.

565
00:37:18,060 --> 00:37:19,690
Well...

566
00:37:20,580 --> 00:37:24,870
I... I will take out my phone and film them.

567
00:37:24,870 --> 00:37:27,630
I will save whoever pays me.

568
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,270
Qi Qi.

569
00:37:32,270 --> 00:37:36,480
Is it because of Cong that you have a grudge against me?

570
00:37:37,180 --> 00:37:39,560
Yes, but not much.

571
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:44,700
It was mainly because you were so close back then. I felt like an outsider.

572
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:47,670
Haven't I told you about this?

573
00:37:48,830 --> 00:37:51,170
Let's not talk about the past then.

574
00:37:52,620 --> 00:37:55,810
What do you think of Jing Xi Chi?

575
00:37:57,020 --> 00:37:58,390
What do you mean?

576
00:37:58,390 --> 00:37:59,620
I mean...

577
00:37:59,620 --> 00:38:01,650
do you think he likes you?

578
00:38:01,650 --> 00:38:03,860
He likes me?

579
00:38:05,220 --> 00:38:07,270
Why would he like me?

580
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:11,700
He and I are just buddies.

581
00:38:11,700 --> 00:38:14,530
Are you two buddies like us?

582
00:38:18,220 --> 00:38:21,750
How... how could we be the same?

583
00:38:21,750 --> 00:38:28,300
Besides, if I liked someone... it definitely wouldn't be Chen Huan Er.

584
00:38:42,770 --> 00:38:44,700
I'll go find her then.

585
00:38:48,660 --> 00:38:50,830
Who are you going to find?

586
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:53,420
Huan Er.

587
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:58,060
Cong.

588
00:38:58,060 --> 00:39:00,040
Jing Xi Chi.

589
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:04,940
I have something to talk to you about.

590
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:09,250
Chen Huan Er.

591
00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:11,750
Cong.

592
00:39:13,620 --> 00:39:15,080
Huan Er.

593
00:39:15,700 --> 00:39:17,560
Well, I have something else to do.

594
