Qi Qi, talk to Cong first.

595
00:39:20,270 --> 00:39:22,180
I got to go.

596
00:39:24,140 --> 00:39:25,530
Huan Er.

597
00:39:26,470 --> 00:39:28,860
I have something to say to you alone.

598
00:39:31,270 --> 00:39:32,960
You and me?

599
00:39:37,830 --> 00:39:40,320
I'll step away then.

600
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:42,790
I also have something to tell you.

601
00:39:46,270 --> 00:39:47,430
Qi Qi.

602
00:39:47,430 --> 00:39:49,180
No, Qi—

603
00:40:07,990 --> 00:40:10,000
What's the matter, Cong?

604
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:13,270
Chen Huan Er.

605
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:16,430
I like you.

606
00:40:33,390 --> 00:40:35,700
What did you say?

607
00:40:35,700 --> 00:40:40,500
You're the most optimistic and cheerful person I've ever met.

608
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:43,790
I've liked you for a long, long time.

609
00:40:43,790 --> 00:40:49,950
I deliberately asked Song Cong questions just to get closer to you.

610
00:40:49,950 --> 00:40:53,310
Now that the exam is over,

611
00:40:53,950 --> 00:40:59,860
