613
00:41:10,210 --> 00:41:15,120
In my eyes, you have always been the most special one.

614
00:41:15,120 --> 00:41:17,170
Huan Er, I'm serious.

615
00:41:17,830 --> 00:41:23,480
I don't want to be Doraemon and be nice to everyone.

616
00:41:24,140 --> 00:41:26,320
I just want to be good to you.

617
00:41:51,350 --> 00:41:56,560
No, Cong. I... I always thought

618
